These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, blues, funk, rock
1. the fan of blues is between the fan of funk and the fan of rock##2
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | rock | blues | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, soy-milk, milk
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | milk | sprite | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, fish, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the dog##2
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | lizard | dog | fish | snake |

